{"word":"ἀερτάζω","slug":"ἀερτάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀερτάζω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀερτάζω'><el>ἀερτάζω</el></a> is a <a href='S:lengthened'>lengthd.</a> epic form of <el>ἀείρω.</el>\n<p/><i>to lift up</i>:— <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a> <el>ἠέρταζον</el>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/>"}]}